      • disk

        @Deprecated
public String disk()
        Deprecated. 
        Returns the name of the disk. The name must be 1-63 characters long and comply with RFC1035. Specifically, the name must match the regular expression [a-z]([-a-z0-9]*[a-z0-9])? which means the first character must be a lowercase letter, and all following characters must be a dash, lowercase letter, or digit, except the last character, which cannot be a dash.
        See Also:
        RFC1035
